data.description: This beautiful 4/3/2 family home in south Lubbock on a quiet cul-de-sac has an open layout in the living, kitchen, and dining areas, vinyl plank flooring throughout, 4 spacious bedrooms plus an office, and a large fenced backyard with a covered patio. Schedule your showing with this beautiful home in this kid and family friendly neighborhood today!
